        High Dynamic Resolution (HDR)
        =============================
        
        Luminance HDR
        -------------
        
        .. _setup-1:
        
        setup
        ~~~~~
        
        .. code:: bash
        
           sudo apt update
           sudo apt install luminance-hdr
        
        settings used to combine a darker and a lighter image 2019-02-24
        ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
        
        -  tonemap
        
           -  operator: Reinhard ’05
           -  brightness: -10
           -  chromatic adaptation: 0
           -  light adaptation: 1
        
        -  process
        
           -  pre-gamma: 0.86
        
